  id: Ominous Lab
  displayName: Ominous Lab
  introText: You stumble upon a derelict laboratory station floating in ominously
    in space. Upon further investigation, you realise it was an illegal genetic testing
    facility. It may still be functional, but the outcome is not guaranteed.
  choices:
  - choiceText: Throw one of your lackeys into the machines.
    outcomeText: One of your crew members is duplicated! 20% chance they die instead.
    effects:
    - effectType: 6
      amount: 0
      secondAmount: 0
      thirdAmount: 0
      percentageOdds: 80
      crewName: 
